OL,3,CComplex dementia patients stuck living
OL,4,Con Jersey wards
OL,6,FITV News can reveal that several
OL,7,Fcomplex dementia patients are stuck
OL,8,Fliving in wards because they have
OL,9,Fnowhere else to go.
OL,11,FAs of October 2024, six people in the
OL,12,Fgeneral hospital are fit to leave but
OL,13,Fare unable to because there is nowhere
OL,14,Fon the island that will give them
OL,15,Fspecialist care for complex dementia.
