OL,4,Con Jersey wards
OL,6,FChief Executive of My Voice, an
OL,7,Findependent advocate for mental health
OL,8,Fin Jersey, Patricia Winchester says:
OL,9,F"What we have is people who are living
OL,10,Fin a clinical environment for months
OL,11,Fand years on end, it's not homely, it
OL,12,Fdoesn't have their personal belongings.
OL,14,F"It's not that the wards are not
OL,15,Ftrying to place them but it is when
OL,16,Fthey are assessed by care homes, they
OL,17,Fsay we can't take on this risk as we
OL,18,Fcan't meet their needs.
