OL,6,F"So, constant conversations are going
OL,7,Fon - but there just aren't enough
OL,8,Fplaces."
OL,10,FCurrently. the six people in the
OL,11,Fhospital may wait for between four to
OL,12,Ffive months on a medical ward because
OL,13,Fthey may have behaviours that are more
OL,14,Fphysically or verbally challenging for
OL,15,Fmainstream care homes.
