OL,3,CComplex dementia patients stuck living
OL,4,Con Jersey wards
OL,6,FWithin the mental health facilities at
OL,7,FSt Saviour, there are an additional
OL,8,Fsix people with complex dementia in
OL,9,FBeech Ward and I've been told there
OL,10,Fare another one or two people in Cedar
OL,11,FWard.
OL,13,FAll need specialist dementia care, but
OL,14,Fthey have been stuck there for a lot
OL,15,Flonger, with one person staying there
OL,16,Ffor more than two years.
