OL,6,FHealth Minister, Chris Bown the
OL,7,Finterim Chief Officer for Health and
OL,8,FAndy Weir the Director of Mental
OL,9,FHealth agreed that a clinical setting
OL,10,Fis not the right place for these
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,FThere is evidence that keeping people
OL,14,Fon a general medical ward for longer
OL,15,Fthan they need to is detrimental to
OL,16,Fboth their physical and mental health.
OL,18,FAndy Weir says that a solution to this
OL,19,Fis now a priority - adding that we
OL,20,Fcan't carry on as we are.
