OL,6,FHe says: "Clearly we can't build a
OL,7,Fnursing and staff a nursing home
OL,8,Ftomorrow, but we have to decide
OL,9,Fwhether or not the state provides
OL,10,Fnursing care provision for more
OL,11,Fcomplex needs with dementia if we're
OL,12,Fnot we have to make sure that capacity
OL,13,Fincreases quickly."
OL,15,FIf you are one of the families
OL,16,Faffected by this issue, we would like
OL,17,Fto hear your story. Please do contact
OL,18,Fus either by emailing
OL,19,Fchannelnews@itv.com or calling us on
OL,20,F01534 480580.
